Sala Astoria-
Authentic Spanish Tapas in Astoria, NY

Step into the vibrant world of Sala Astoria in the heart of Astoria, Queens! Since our beginning on the Bowery in 1999, our mission has been to transport you to an authentic Spanish experience. By authentic, we mean offering you a warm, inviting experience that lovingly pays tribute to the rich history of genuine Spanish cuisine.

We offer a menu full of classic tapas, paella, and fine wines served in a casual, elegant space. Whether you're joining us for dinner, a special celebration, or a private event, Sala Astoria brings the spirit of Spain to New York in every plate and every gathering.

Come visit us!

PINCHOS, TAPAS, PAELLA AND MORE

At Sala, we devote the "tapas" section of our menu to the vast world of pinchos. However, the core of our culinary offerings unfolds in the numerous choices within our "raciones" section—delightful dishes crafted for sharing among small or large groups. In addition to our pinchos and raciones, our menu is further enriched by hearty Platos, authentic Paella, Arroces, and a sweet finale with our inviting Postres. Explore the true Spanish flavors that cater to every palate.
